PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of Bernard Ghert, of Willowdale, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Paul Morton, whose term has expired.
